CREATE EXPRESS SERVER THAT HAS SPECIFIC ROUTES
MAKE GET REQUEST TO THE REQUIRED API SERVICE PROVIDERS - LIKE IMDB API OR TMDB API ETC
MANIPULATE RESPONSE FROM THESE API TO GET THE REQUIRED DATA - like fetch all - fetch first x - fetch in a given range - ALL THESE ARE DONE BY IDENTIFYING THE PARAMS IN THE URL 

AT MAX CAN MAKE 100 REQUESTS TO IMDB API PER DAY - 
SO MAKE REQUESTS USING MULTIPLE ACCOUNTS OR THREADS
Used accounts - see in dotenv file with their passwords